description:
This song is dedicated to supporting the 𝗜𝗠𝗕𝗔 𝗞𝗪𝗔 𝗔𝗞𝗜𝗟𝗜 𝗖𝗼𝗻𝗰𝗲𝗿𝘁, taking place on June 9th, 2024, at KICC. All proceeds from the concert will contribute to the construction of ᴘᴀʀᴋʟᴀɴᴅꜱ ꜱᴅᴀ ᴄʜᴜʀᴄʜ.

You can purchase tickets on the TICKETSASA website via the following link: [https://www.ticketsasa.com/events/eventdetail/view/4012/hapa_ni_wapi_gospel_concert](https://www.ticketsasa.com/events/eventdetail/view/4012/hapa_ni_wapi_gospel_concert).

Neno Litasimama [ This world will pass but the WORD of God will remain forever more, Amen]
